<div>


<p>
You are at the platonic solid market.  You are allowed to purchase any (non-negative) number of each type of solid.  You wish to create a:  
</p>

<p style='color:green'>
Shopping basket which contains V vertices, E edges, and F faces.
</p>

<p style='color:blue'>
A tetrahedron has 4 vertices, 6 edges, and 4 faces.
</p>

<p style='color:gold'>
A cube has 8 vertices, 12 edges, and 6 faces.
</p>


<p style='color:red'>
An octahedron has 6 vertices, 12 edges, and 8 faces.
</p>

<p>
Use the up and down arrows to add or subtract each type of solid from your shopping basket to answer the following questions. If there is no solution (or the only solution is an empty basket) submit an empty basket:


</div>

<div id="question">


Click the "Start" button when you are ready to begin.



